💡 Key Insights & Findings

Based on the dashboard analysis:

Overall Performance: The total revenue generated is $1.20M across 8,523 items, with an average sale value of $141 and an average customer rating of 3.9/5.
Top Categories:Fruits and Vegetables and Snack Foods are the top-selling item categories.
Location Dominance:Tier 3 locations generated the highest sales compared to Tier 1 and Tier 2.
Customer Preferences: Products with Low Fat content are strongly preferred and generate higher sales volume compared to regular fat products.
Outlet Type: 'Supermarket Type 3' and medium-sized outlets drive the most significant portion of the total revenue.
